race.comment: POWER OF THE BRAVE (2) talented gelding with his hoof on the till. Chased hard with the 59kg when a tiring fourth over 1100m at Canterbury. Assess on his narrow second to Sunrise three starts back at this track and trip. EXTRAVAGENT LAD (4) back to his preferred trip and will benefit with McMurray's 2kg claim. Covered plenty of ground in the run with the 60.5kg when a plugging eighth over 1100m at Canterbury. Gets a better set-up and not to be underestimated. WHO BUT ROO (6) tough old gelding racing in career best form. Closed quickly for an unlucky third over 1100m at Canterbury. Can surprise some of his more fancied rivals. INDEFENSIBLE (8) was spot them all a start on straightening but should be very strong late.
